name: Sponsor an Empowerment Wristband!
description:
Would you like to empower a child being bullied?  Here's your chance! For as little as $5, you can get a Free2Luv empowerment wristband into the hands and heart of a child suffering from bullying.  With 1 out of every 4 children being bullied, our goal is to end this epidemic by raising youth's self-esteem and encouraging them to speak out, stand up and let their voices be heard. 

You can either suggest someone you know who is being bullied or we'll give a band to someone who has reached out to us.

Thank you for participating in our Friends Don't Let Friends Bully WE CARE Program!  Together, we are making a difference in the lives of youth.

Another way to participate in WE CARE is by shopping with us because every time you shop, we gift an empowerment band to another child.
